def get_R(channels,N,n,m, block_total):
    
    R = np.zeros((N, 1), dtype=int)
    
    for each_channel in channels:
        
        for block in range(block_total):
            
            index = random.randint(1, n-9)
            
            sub_channel = each_channel[index:index+N,:m]
            
            R = np.concatenate((R, sub_channel), axis=1)
            
    return R[:,1:]
            

N = 8
n = X_R.shape[0]
m = X_R.shape[1]
block_total = 3

R = get_R([X_R, X_G, X_B], N, n, m, block_total)

print(R.shape)

def ICA_func(Z, rho):
    
    n = Z.shape[0]
    N = Z.shape[1]
    
    I = np.identity(n)
    W = np.identity(n)
    Y = np.matmul(W,Z)
    
    while len(set(np.round(np.matmul(np.tanh(Y), np.power(Y, 3).T).diagonal(),5))) != 1:
        
        delta_W = np.matmul((N*I - np.matmul(np.tanh(Y), np.power(Y, 3).T)), W)
        
        W = W + rho*delta_W
        
        Y = np.matmul(W,Z)
        
    return W

learning_rate = 0.000001
    
output = ICA_func(Z, learning_rate)

Function to find SNR¶

In [1673]:
def SNR_func(S, S_new):
    
    original_sum = np.sum(np.square(S))
    diff_sum = np.sum(np.square(np.subtract(S,S_new)))
    
    snr = 10*np.log10(original_sum/diff_sum)
    
    return snr
In [1674]:
output = SNR_func(sig_piano,S_recovered)

print(output)
